# .gitignore — Social Media Skills

## Secrets and credentials
*.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*token*
*secret*
*key*
*.pem
*.p12
*.ghp*

## OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini

## Editor files
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.idea/
.vscode/
*.sublime-*

## Build artifacts
node_modules/
dist/
build/
*.pyc
__pycache__/

## Temporary files
*.tmp
*.bak

## Local Hermes data (never commit)
.usage.json
.usage.json.lock
.curator_state
.curator_backups/
.hub/
